<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-03-05T21:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-03-05T21:00:00-05:00" n="60" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d60">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">033.1110 Wallace, Henry A./128f: Circular
                            telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to Certain <gloss type="to">Diplomatic
                                    Representatives in the American Republics</gloss></hi><note n="6" xml:id="d60fn6">The Ambassadors in Panama, Chile, Bolivia,
                                Peru, Ecuador, and Colombia and the Minister in Costa
                            Rica.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-05T22:00:00-04:00">March 5, 1943—10
                                p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The itinerary of the Vice President is as follows: <table cols="4" rendition="#nowrap" rows="54">
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Costa
                                        Rica</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Wednesday</cell>
                                    <cell>March 17</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Miami</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">6:15 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Balboa</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">12:50 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Thursday</cell>
                                    <cell>March 18</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Balboa</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">9:30 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive San José</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:20 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Sunday</cell>
                                    <cell>March 21</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave San José</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">12:45 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive David</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">3:00 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Monday</cell>
                                    <cell>March 22</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave David</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">3:15 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Balboa, C.Z. (Panama
                                        City)</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">4:45 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <pb facs="0070" n="58" xml:id="pg_58"/>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Chile</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Wednesday</cell>
                                    <cell>March 24</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Balboa</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">1:15 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Cali, Colombia (En route to
                                        Santiago)</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">4:30 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Thursday</cell>
                                    <cell>March 25</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Cali</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">7:30 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Lima, Peru (En route to
                                        Santiago)</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">4:15 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Friday</cell>
                                    <cell>March 26</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Lima</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">5:30 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Santiago, Chile</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">5:35 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Friday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 2</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Santiago</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">6:45 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Antofagasta</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:20 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Bolivia</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Sunday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 4</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Antofagasta</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:35 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Arequipa (En route to La
                                        Paz)</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">2:10 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Monday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 5</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Arequipa</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">8:45 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive La Paz</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">12:45 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Thursday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 8</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave La Paz</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:50 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Oruro</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">12:40 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Friday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 9</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Oruro</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">1:00 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Cochabamba</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">1:35 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Saturday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 10</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Cochabamba</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:00 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive La Paz</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:40 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Peru</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Saturday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 10</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave La Paz</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:50 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Lima</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">3:55 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Ecuador</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Thursday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 15</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Lima</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">6:30 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Guayaquil (Ecuador) (En route
                                        to Quito)</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">12:05 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Guayaquil</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">12:20 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Quito</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">1:40 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Monday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 19</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Quito</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">7:45 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Guayaquil</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">10:00 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Colombia</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Tuesday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 20</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Guayaquil</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">12:25 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Cali, Colombia (En route to
                                        Bogotá)</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">3:25 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Cali</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">4:00 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Bogotá</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">5:25 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Thursday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 22</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Bogotá</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">7:45 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Cali</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">9:10 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Friday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 23</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Cali</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:45 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Medellin</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">1:35 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <pb facs="0071" n="59" xml:id="pg_59"/>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Return</hi></cell>
                                    <cell/>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Saturday</cell>
                                    <cell>April 24</cell>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Medellin</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:30 a.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Balboa</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">2:15 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Leave Balboa</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">2:35 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#hanging">Arrive Miami</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">11:00 p.m.</cell>
                                </row>
                            </table></p>
                        <p>All flights will be made by commercial plane.</p>
                        <p>A separate telegram<note n="7" xml:id="d60fn7">Not printed.</note>
                            follows with respect to suggestions of visits Mr. Wallace would like to
                            make.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>